{"title":"念泗桥","authors":["刘春阳"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":1,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"念泗桥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘春阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少个痴情者"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沿着谜一般的小巷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弯弯曲曲地寻找"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寻找你——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了证实一则玉人吹箫的童话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，你凝固了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝固成一段"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风十里又尽江南的历史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯有流水，唯有洞箫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无暇顾盼疑惑的眼神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依旧日日地流，夜夜地吹……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其实，人们又何必"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反反复复，复复反反地寻觅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥头不是二分明月吗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桥畔的琼花也正在吐香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨光熹微，一个多彩的古城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旋转在洞箫的音律里"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}